snippet.title: Ya Zahra | Mesum Abbas | Bibi Fatima Noha 2025 | Hussain Faisal | Ayyam e Fatimiyah
snippet.description:
"Ya Zahra , Mazlooma Masooma" 

Urdu Noha x Arabic Latmiya - 2 languages, 2 cultures - 1 grief - Ya Zahra (sa)
“دو ثقافتیں، ایک صدا — یا زہرا (س)”
@MesumAbbas ft. @hussainfaisal 

Listen to the latest Bibi Fatima Noha 2025 by Mesum Abbas for Ayyam e Fatima - Shahadat Bibi Fatima (sa).
Topic: Ayam e Fatima 2025 - Shahadat Bibi Fatima
Mesum Abbas releases his latest Bibi Fatima Noha for Ayyam e Fatima 2025 titled “Ya Zahra” after Ya Fatima.

The noha “Ya Zahra (sa)” is a unique and historic collaboration between Syed Mesum Abbas, a renowned Urdu nohakhwan, and Mulla Hussain Faisal, a respected Iraqi radood based in Bahrain.

For the first time, an Urdu kalam has been recited fully in an Iraqi andaaz, bringing together two powerful traditions of aza:

Urdu language × Iraqi style of recitation

Recorded entirely in Bahrain/USA, this kalam carries the depth of Iraqi recitation and the emotional power of Urdu poetry, combining them into one heartfelt expression of the grief of Bibi Fatima-tuz-Zahra (sa).

This noha reflects a simple truth:
Azadari is not limited to one culture, one people, or one style — it unites all lovers of Bibi Zahra (as).

Mesum Abbas releases his latest Bibi Fatima Noha for Ayyam e Fatima 2025 titled “Ya Zahra” after Ya Fatima.

YA ZAHRA sa | یازھرا

Originally Recited & Composed by
Shahid Hussain Baltistani

Written By
Janab Mazhar Abidi & Janab Shahid Hussain Baltistani

Baqar Ali Baltistani

Muharram Album | Jamad ul Awal  2025 / 1447
Releasing Date | 14 Nov 2025


Lyrics:
---------

Fatima Zahra s.a , Fatima Zahra s.a

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a

Aey Meri Bibi Teray Dar Pay Istghasa Hay 
Tera Mamnoon Meri Shahzadi Ye Jahan Saara Hay 

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a

Tu Hamain Hifz Aur Amaan’n Day Day 
Apni Chadar Ka Saibaan Day Day 
Teri Qudrat Mein Kia Nahi Bibi 
Tu Jisay Chahay Do Jahan Day Day

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a

Tujh Ko Ummat Nay Yun Sataya Hay 
Marg E Mohsin Pay Bhi Rulaya Hay 
Tujh Ko Baba Kay Baad Ummat Nay 
Haey Darbaar Main Bulaya Hay 

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a

Boli Zahra Ali a.s Say Ya Maula 
Ghum Ye Mujh Say Nahi Saha Jata 
Qatl E Mohsin Say Barh K Mushkil Tha 
Bharay Darbaar Main Mera Jana 

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a 

Jab Tha Rassi Main Murtaza a.s Ka Gala 
Imtehaan Zabt Ka Wo Tha Tera 
Haan Madina Ujar Gaya Hota 
Tu Ho Say Deti Bad Dua Zahra

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a

Tu Hijaab E Khuda Hay Ya Zahra s.a
Dard Teray Hain Sab Say Poshida 
Kitni Muztar Hay Kitni Zakhmi Hay 
Ya Ali a.s Jantay Hain Ya Fizza s.a

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a 
 
Aey Mohammad saww Ki Laadli Dukhtar 
Ghum Main Teray Hay Murtaza a.s Muztar 
Jis Nay Dhaaya Tha Baab Khaybar Ka 
Gir Gaya Khaak Per Wo Ye Keh Kar 

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a

Hum Ko Her Aan Ye Nadamat Hay 
Hum Hain Mujrim Teri Adalat Hay 
Rizq Aulaad Zindagi Her Pal 
Jo Bhi Kuch Hay Teri Badolat Hay

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a

Qarz Makrooz Ka Ada Karde
Muflison Ka Naseeb Wah Krde
Jin Ki Gaudi Hari Ahi Bibi
Unko Aulaad Tu Ataa Karde

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a

Waqt E Akhir Hay Bus Mera Bibi 
Anginat Hain Meray Gunaah Bibi 
Wasta Tujh Ko Teray Bachon Ka 
Bakhshwana Meray Gunaah Bibi 

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a

Farsh E Majlis Pay Aur Musallay Per 
Her Jawan Keh Raha Hay Ro Ro Kar 
Hum Rahain Na Rahain Magar Bibi 
Ta Qayamat Rahay Ghum E Sarwar 

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a

Aey Meri Bibi Teray Bachon Ka Ghum Maantay Hain
Apni Aulad Say Kahin Bath K Ghum Ye Pyara Hay

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a

Gharq e Matam Shud, Alam E Baala
Mirawad Maula, Sarwar E Zahra
Aah O Waa Wailaa, Aah O Waa Wailaa

Jahan afsaanay bune jaate hain, aur har drop, har rotation, aur har clutch moment ka apni wuqat bayan krta hai!

Grand Finals tak ka safar har match ke saath aur mushkil hota jae ga, to apni kursi ki peti baandh lijiye, snacks haath mein lijiye, aur tayyar ho jaiye ek aur din k world class PUBG MOBILE action k liye! 🏆🔥

Is saal ka format dobara badla gaya hai taa k shaiqeen aur waqar k peche bhagny wali teamain dono ko zyada lutf haasil ho.
Pehla bara twist ""The Gauntlet Stage"" hai, 
Duniya ki 16 behtareen teamain yahan bary dao laga kr muqabla karen gi.
Dao Pech? Har mumkin lagaye jayen gy.

Rank 1 ta 7: Seedha Grand Finals mein pohanch jayen gi.
Rank 8 ta 16: Group Stage se ek aur mauqa hasil ho ga.

Group Stage mai har group se upper ki 3 teamain seedha Grand Finals ke liye qualify kr jayen gi.
Jo teamain 4th–11th par thin unko Last Chance khelny ka akhri mauqa mile ga.
Lekin jo 12th–16th par aayegi, unka 2025 PMGC ka safar yahin khatam ho jayega.
Aakhir mein, Last Chance (Dec 6 ta 7) teamon k liye aakhri parao hoga.

Yahan do din, or do mawaqy hongy.
Top 2 spots hasil karen, ya shaiqeen k sath beth kr Grand Finals ka nazara dekhen.

Khush aamdeed, 2025 PUBG MOBILE GLOBAL CHAMPIONSHIP Mai — Jahan sarbulandi hasil krny k liye ek Faisla Kun Jung Hogi!
